{
  "stem": "3165.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then they took away their sons to the Ukraine and to the Ukrainian police, I guess, you know, because they were young Ukrainian guys and they-- and I heard that they were drafted.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I remember I didn't see them anymore of this house.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And now I'm looking after all these cattle.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And of course, they would serve enough food, and they'd have a lot of-- they'd have bacon and ham.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I knew I mustn't.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That's not kosher.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I mustn't eat that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And at the table, you know, and they-- and they must know I'm Jewish.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "If I won't eat that, they will know right away I'm Jewish.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I would put on my plate and pretend I'm eating it and just throw it under the table.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So they-- they won't see it, because I would sweep up later on.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I would do the housework after.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So I knew I'm safe, because I'm going to sweep it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I'd eat every-- the vegetable, whatever, potato.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But I was so-- it was so in me that I knew I can't eat no kosher, no bacon or ham, no matter how hungry I was.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And now I'm thinking-- I'm thinking about my sister.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What did I do?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Where is she?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How is she?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I would go on the field.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And one day I would go on the field with the cattle, and I-- I was thinking of my sister, and I started to cry so loud.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then I thought, what did I do?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Where is she?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, how am I going to find her now?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I cried very, very loud.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then from the far, I saw a lady.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "From far away, I saw a lady walking towards me.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
